    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo quinquagesimo tertio, quarto idus iulii, indictione
                        quintadecima. Manifesti sumus nos <persName><name ref="Cheroinus"
                                >Cheroinus</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Cheroellus"
                                >Cheroellus</name></persName> germani filii quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Calefinus">Caleffini</name></persName> quia (…) per hanc
                        cartulam offertionis, pro remedio anime predicti patris nostri et pro
                        remedio anime nostre, per visionem predicti patris offerimus tibi deo et
                            <orgName key="#Rivers #Bridges/pontoons #Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3209"><rs key="#Bridges/pontoons">ponti</rs> et
                                <rs key="#Hospitals">hospitali</rs> de <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >Arno</rs></orgName> videlicet integram nostram portionem unius petie
                        terre que est posita in loco qui vocatur <placeName>Poio
                            Alberichi</placeName>, que tenet unum caput in via, aliut caput tenet in
                        terra prenominati pontis, latus unum tenet in terra de <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3200"><rs key="#Monasteries"
                                >monasterio</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Rivers #Bridges/pontoons #Monasteries #Hospitals"
                                ref="#places/3200">Ficeclense</placeName></orgName>, aliut latus
                        tenet in terra filiorum <persName><name ref="Giutus"
                        >Ciuti</name></persName>. Competit exinde nobis quartam portionem. (…)
                            <foreign>Pena in duplum</foreign> et insuper penam argienti optimi
                        soldorum centum. (…) Actum in capite predicti pontis. Singna manuum
                        prenominati germani qui hanc offertionis cartulam fieri rogaverunt. Singna
                        manuum <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Vecchio">Vecchi</name></persName>
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Sichelmus">Sichelmi</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Tiniosus">Tineosi</name></persName>
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Malagalgia">Malagalgie</name></persName>
                        et <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Alcherius">Alcarini</name></persName>
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Dominicus">Dominici</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Alexius">Allexii</name></persName>
                        filii quondam <persName><name ref="Bellinus">Bellini</name></persName> et
                        aliorum plurimum rogatorum <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S) <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Hubertus">Hubertus</name></persName>
                        donni inperatoris <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> post traditam complevi et
                        dedi.</ab>
                </div>
